casebody.data:
The ESTATE OF Francis P. KENNEDY, (Frederick Kennedy and Gabriel A. Yandoli, Co-Executors), et al., Plaintiffs-Petitioners,
v.
Stuart A. ROSENBLATT, CPA, et al., Defendants-Respondents. C-666 September Term 2018
082206 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 8, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001368-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
